Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:15.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:23.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:27.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:34.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:38.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:45.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:52.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:56.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:04.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:08.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:15.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:19.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx140\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,170.389)}Enroll in the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}Gel Shocker Terror School!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You have been chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:57.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You will now join\NCentipede Tiger's Terror School!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I would be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter will join Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster... give Wakako back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Resistance is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The message tube is empty again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the eighth one this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kid Corps are slacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kid Corps are made up of\NJapan's most accomplished boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't just mess up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chairman... you think something\Ncould have happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think that, go write\Ndown pigeons' numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the addresses of their owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I need your instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I already did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious, too. I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These kids all live\Nin the Tanzawa District.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's convenient for our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If they've sent combatants,\Na cyborg will soon follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like an insect...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Centipede Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be here, cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We have one goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To create a new organization\Nwithin Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And their first task will be to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A new organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Presenting, the first class\Nof the Gel Shocker Terror School!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tanzawa District members\Nof the Rider Kid Corps...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your new organization... could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce Gel Shocker's\Nnew organization, the Gel Shocker Kid Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, Kishi! Hirai! Ota!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, Gel Shocker has brainwashed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him, children Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as we taught you in Terror School!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! I'll handle the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You go after Centipede Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Tiger... return\Nthe children to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it vex you, Hongo Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, Gel Shocker will have every member\Nof the Rider Kid Corps under our control!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already outside the Rider\NKid Corps headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, they're after HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him, Gel Shocker Kid Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My power is greater than Rider's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Naoki and Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're both safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you'd better stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman... run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I run to, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They got to you, too... Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the Chairman\Nof the Kamen Rider Kid Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Chairman of the\NGel Shocker Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... you too will join\Nthe Gel Shocker Kid Corps, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider Kid Corps\Nheadquarters will become
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the headquarters of the\NGel Shocker Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost done...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo, I'm Tatsuji Yamanobu\Nof the Rider Kid Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a part of the Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Gel Shocker is after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to run, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave an injured man behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, let's take him to\Nthe shed around back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hang in there!\N- Run away... run away, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji, hold him steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis... I don't think anyone followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did an injured man enter here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No... no one's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk! Confess, or I kill the boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, don't tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the Rider Kid Corps!\NWe fight for peace and justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace and justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really more important\Nthan your brother's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:10:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, but I can't just let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The shed out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy... I'll bring you to join\NGel Shocker's Terror School as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi... I'll burn you\Nto death inside that shed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,An underground storehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:34.70,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They burned him to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Mr. Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to save my brother so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't wrong at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Human life is more important\Nthan even peace and justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll bring Tatsuji back to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,on my name as the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliantly done, General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi has died in agony,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll turn all of the Rider\NKid Corps into the Gel Shocker Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Tiger's Terror\NSchool will train them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll send them to incite\Ndestruction all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As Gel Shocker combatants,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they must follow the rule\Nand take the gelper drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already seen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bringing the gelper\Ndrug to the Terror School.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's ironclad rule:\Nthe gelper drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once taken, it must be taken again\Nevery three hours, or the user will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:38.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a horrifying drug used by\NGel Shocker to guard against betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the kids in here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Always aim to penetrate\Nthe heart of the adversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's kill class is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With the new arrivals, our initial\Nclass is up to fourteen members!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to swear\Nyour loyalty to Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The first article of the\NGel Shocker Children's Charter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring chaos and evil to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace and justice are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, sit down and enjoy your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it contain the gelper drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a special lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The gelper drug should put them to sleep\Nfor an hour the moment it's taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure you\Nput the gelper drug in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What those children\Nare eating is mere flour!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no gelper drug in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them, child combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Captain of the\NGel Shocker Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... they've gotten to you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... you have no allies left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Corps HQ is now Gel Shocker Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one more move, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I give the order, the children die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One word from me, and the\Nchildren will all jump off the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to let that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Tiger... what is it you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The children's lives are irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... do as you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider can't fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deal the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.54,Italics,,0,0,0,,I cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:31.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,If I don't defeat Centipede Tiger,\Nhe'll control the children forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Hammer Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump! Jump, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was having a nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Taki! Captain Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... are you all back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where's Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find him, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider died\Ndestroying Centipede Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker must take\Nadvantage of this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, future hope of Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:55.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To save the Kamen Rider Kid Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:59.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider exploded with\Nthe powerful enemy, Centipede Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:01.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is Kamen Rider still\Nout there somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:06.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And what was the shadow that\Nwe saw inside Gel Shocker's base?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,70,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(277.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassins sent by\NGel Shocker to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:18.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,are the fake Kamen Rider\Nand the monstrous Flytrap Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As an Anti-Shocker Alliance made up\Nof Gel Shocker's victims comes to light,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:26.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider will face the Shocker\NRider in a deadly Cyclone match.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:31.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for\N"Evil! The Fake Kamen Rider"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:31.16,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}Evil! The Fake Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:39.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:46.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:50.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:54.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:24:01.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:06.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:12.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Enroll in the\NGel Shocker Terror School!!